title: DDFP 331: Jameis Winston reaction & NFC South
itunes:title: DDFP 331: Jameis Winston reaction & NFC South
description:
Shek is joined by NFL Media's Kyle Montgomery to discuss Jameis Winston's combine press conference and debate his pro comparison. The guys also enter the "Elimination Chamber" discussing the NFC South and NFL events before Shek reveals another childhood basketball story.
